snippet.title: Borderwatch : Dark Armada - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Borderwatch: Dark Armada is now on Steam. Wishlist  NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2260100/Borderwatch_Dark_Armada/

As part of the Borderwatch team, collect, defend, and survive against hordes of zombies in this 3rd person action horror survival game!

Build your team, Loot, and Survive!
